<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>TWZ</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 02:33:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>沙特获准购买多达 20,000 枚激光制导火箭</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/saudis-cleared-to-buy-a-whopping-20000-laser-guided-rockets</link><description>&lt;p&gt;沙特人显然正在武装自己，以防御未来冲突中大量无人机的袭击。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/saudis-cleared-to-buy-a-whopping-20000-laser-guided-rockets"&gt;沙特阿拉伯获准购买多达 20,000 枚激光制导火箭的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 01:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/saudis-cleared-to-buy-a-whopping-20000-laser-guided-rockets</guid></item><item><title>以下是美国海军军舰可用于支持对伊朗的封锁</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/here-are-the-u-s-navy-warships-available-to-support-the-blockade-of-iran</link><description>&lt;p&gt;包括两个航母战斗群和一个两栖战备群在内的20多艘美国海军军舰正在中东地区执行任务。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/here-are-the-u-s-navy-warships-available-to-support-the-blockade-of-iran"&gt;是美国海军军舰可用于支持对伊朗的封锁，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 23:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/here-are-the-u-s-navy-warships-available-to-support-the-blockade-of-iran</guid></item><item><title>英国“没有购买”用于核用途的 F-35A：英国皇家空军</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/uk-did-not-buy-f-35a-for-nuclear-role-raf</link><description>&lt;p&gt;该声明给英国计划如何恢复其北约核打击作用带来了新的不确定性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/uk-did-not-buy-f-35a-for-nuclear-role-raf"&gt;英国“没有购买”F-35A 核角色：英国皇家空军的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 19:32:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/uk-did-not-buy-f-35a-for-nuclear-role-raf</guid></item><item><title>美国恢复对伊朗港口封锁的第一天爆发新的袭击（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/first-full-day-of-resumed-u-s-blockade-on-iranian-ports-erupts-in-new-attacks</link><description>&lt;p&gt;除了打击伊朗目标外，中央司令部还拒绝了两艘试图突破新封锁的船只。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/first-full-day-of-resumed-u-s-blockade-on-iranian-ports-erupts-in-new-attacks"&gt;美国对伊朗港口恢复封锁的第一天在新的攻击中爆发（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 18:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/first-full-day-of-resumed-u-s-blockade-on-iranian-ports-erupts-in-new-attacks</guid></item><item><title>YFQ-44A Fury“战斗机无人机”发射了第一枚 AIM-120 AMRAAM 导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/yfq-44a-fury-fighter-drone-has-fired-its-first-aim-120-amraam-missile</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这也是美国协同作战飞机无人机首次发射实弹空对空导弹。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/yfq-44a-fury-fighter-drone-has-fired-its-first-aim-120-amraam-missile"&gt;YFQ-44A Fury“战斗机无人机”发射了第一枚 AIM-120 AMRAAM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;导弹&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 18:18:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/yfq-44a-fury-fighter-drone-has-fired-its-first-aim-120-amraam-missile</guid></item><item><title>中国到底有多少架歼20巨龙战斗机？</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/how-many-j-20-stealth-fighters-does-china-actually-have</link><description>&lt;p&gt;焦点可能集中在第六代设计上，但 J-20 巨龙正在通过纯粹的生产规模改变解放军空军。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;帖子&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/how-many-j-20-stealth-fighters-does-china-actually-have"&gt;中国到底有多少架歼20巨龙战斗机？&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 17:55:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/how-many-j-20-stealth-fighters-does-china-actually-have</guid></item><item><title>美国空军计划通过新交易提前五年购买 28,000 枚低成本巡航导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-plans-to-buy-28000-low-cost-cruise-missiles-in-five-years-advance-with-new-deals</link><description>&lt;p&gt;五角大楼正在推进大量采购防区外武器，其成本只是高端传统武器的一小部分。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-plans-to-buy-28000-low-cost-cruise-missiles-in-five-years-advance-with-new-deals"&gt;美国空军计划通过新交易提前五年购买 28,000 枚低成本巡航导弹&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 16:54:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-plans-to-buy-28000-low-cost-cruise-missiles-in-five-years-advance-with-new-deals</guid></item><item><title>美国空军加油机从以色列最大机场启动会影响作战能力吗？</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/will-usaf-tankers-getting-the-boot-from-israels-biggest-airpor-impact-combat-capabilities</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国空军已经在本古里安机场抽调了大部分最大的加油机力量，现在更多的喷气式飞机将不得不寻找新家。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/will-usaf-tankers-getting-the-boot-from-israels-biggest-airpor-impact-combat-capabilities"&gt;美国空军加油机从以色列最大的机场获得启动会影响作战能力吗？&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 23:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/will-usaf-tankers-getting-the-boot-from-israels-biggest-airpor-impact-combat-capabilities</guid></item><item><title>特朗普威胁要袭击伊朗镐山地堡的“前门”，凸显了打击目标的挑战</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/trumps-threat-to-strike-irans-pickaxe-mountain-bunkers-front-door-underscores-targeting-challenges</link><description>&lt;p&gt;镐山是伊朗最难到达的设施，特朗普说他可能“在前门开枪”不太可能只是闲聊。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/trumps-threat-to-strike-irans-pickaxe-mountain-bunkers-front-door-underscores-targeting-challenges"&gt;特朗普威胁要袭击伊朗镐山地堡的“前门”，凸显了目标挑战&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 21:44:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/trumps-threat-to-strike-irans-pickaxe-mountain-bunkers-front-door-underscores-targeting-challenges</guid></item><item><title>韩国将通过全球 6500 架喷气式干扰机大幅增强电子攻击能力</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/south-korea-to-get-huge-electronic-attack-boost-with-global-6500-jammer-jets</link><description>&lt;p&gt;大韩航空将改装两架环球 6500 喷气式飞机，大幅增强首尔的主权电子战能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/south-korea-to-get-huge-electronic-attack-boost-with-global-6500-jammer-jets"&gt;韩国将通过全球 6500 喷气式干扰机获得巨大的电子攻击增强效果的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 18:40:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/south-korea-to-get-huge-electronic-attack-boost-with-global-6500-jammer-jets</guid></item></channel></rss>